'''雷内·里卡德'''（{{lang-en|Albert Napoleon Rene Ricard}}，{{bd|1946年|7月23日|2014年|2月1日|catIdx=Ricard}}），是一名[[美国|美国]]诗人、演员、艺术评论家和画家。

他出生于美国[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]][[波士顿市|波士顿市]]，18岁成为[[安迪·沃霍尔|安迪·沃霍尔]]的门徒。之后出演于1965年的《厨房》、1966年《{{link-en|雀西女郎|Chelsea Girls}}》、1966年《{{link-en|安迪·沃霍尔的故事|The Andy Warhol Story}}》，之后担任《{{link-en|艺术论坛|Artforum}}》的编辑。他还是一名公开的同性恋者<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://vitoschnabel.com/artists/rene---ricard|title=Rene Ricard biography|work=vitoschnabel.com|accessdate=February 15, 2014|archive-date=2014-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140216205544/http://vitoschnabel.com/artists/rene---ricard|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=STM>Levy, Ariel 'New York Storeys' ''The Sunday Times Magazine'', March 25, 2007, pp. 40-51. p. 47</ref><ref name="Hamilton2010">{{cite book|author=Ed Hamilton|title=Legends of the Chelsea Hotel: Living with the Artists and Outlaws in New York's Rebel Mecca|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=I8kzFfwR-t4C&pg=PA286|year=2010|publisher=Da Capo Press|isbn=0-306-82000-5|pages=286–|access-date=2014-02-19|archive-date=2016-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412104539/https://books.google.com/books?id=I8kzFfwR-t4C&pg=PA286|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年2月1日，他因[[癌症|癌症]]去世，享年67岁<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/news/rene-ricard-poet-painter-art-critic-and-warhol-superstar-dead-20140201|title=Rene Ricard, Poet, Painter, Art Critic and Warhol Superstar, Dead|date=February 1, 2014|publisher=''[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]''|accessdate=February 15, 2014|archive-date=2018-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180528052715/https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/news/rene-ricard-poet-painter-art-critic-and-warhol-superstar-dead-20140201|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

